summary: Small area with a castle ready to be cluttered

[/font]

Dawnleaf Creek Castle is a small castle surrounded by a group of mountains
and a river used like a moat...
The mod only shows the exterior cell since I'm not allowed to make the interior
cell of the castle because my "Thesis" it's absorbing my time.
Maybe with the past of the days i will work in the castle but now I like to make 
this public for the use of the community...
Modders can do whatever they want with the castle, I give free permission to edit it...

-Its not navmesh yet!
-For acces to the cell open the console and type Coc 01aaamainentrance

[font=Palatino Linotype][color=#c0504d][size=5][b]Features[/b][/size][/color][/font]

-Keep, walls and some towers
-Outside camp
-Shipyard [size=2]

[/size][font=Palatino Linotype][color=#c0504d][size=5][b]Requeriments
[/b][/size][/color][/font]You need the last version of skyrim, Dawnguard & Dragonborn DLC's
